{"tid":1364420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港球證界有嘢講","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:12:43.000Z","uid":36494,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9c9421e753a1871e0a52efded53c302af4eb9f","tid":1364420,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"致香港人：<br />\n<br />\n香港球證一直希望以熱情以及專業能力，為各層面的足球比賽提供一個公平的競技環境，讓作賽球員可盡情發揮技術，為球迷提供精彩的球賽。<br />\n<br />\n回到場外，球證們同樣相信社會要明確地 #拒絕黑哨、#拒絕白色恐怖，還香港一個公平、公正、公義的環境，使人民能夠在生活中得到保障、發揮所長。<br />\n<br />\n香港足總註冊球證在此表明，廖國文言論不代表我，支持示威者五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n■ 五大訴求 ■<br />\n<br />\n一：徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二：釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n三：撤回612暴動定性<br />\n四：追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五：立即實行雙普選！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZRYvm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZRYvm1.png&h=08908a47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3ramtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3ramtM.png&h=c82dc84f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OThQmtO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOThQmtO.png&h=18b8776c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1729ca326e1bde411cf7fdc276c4cd49a233a68","tid":1364420,"uid":36494,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R3erEfT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3erEfT.png&h=c4cc0bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LzfxA0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LzfxA0.png&h=83a62f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjECLV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjECLV3.png&h=9f0687b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEx8SA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEx8SA7.png&h=178b4c34&s={SIZE}\" /><i